            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a dry large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong>&nbsp;<span class=\"text-highlight\">lamb mince</span></strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until crispy,&nbsp;breaking up with a wooden spoon as you go&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
